Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.40,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,似合ってるよ　その服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clothes look good on you.
