Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:37.83,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who are you dressed as?
