Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.49,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかったら　記念にどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.74,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いけません　いけません
